casebody.data:
Theresa JONES, et al., petitioners,
v.
UNITED STATES. No. 18-981. Supreme Court of the United States May 20, 2019.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied. Justice THOMAS, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent for the reasons set out in Daniel v. United States, 587 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 1713, --- L.Ed.2d ---- (2019) (Thomas, J., dissenting from denial of certiorari).
